          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπο-νίζω</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπονίπτω</span>), aor. imp. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπονιψατε</span>, part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπονίψαντες</span>, mid. pres. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπονίπτεσθαι</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπονιψάμενοι</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">wash off, wash clean</span>, mid.,
          oneself or from oneself; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπονίψαντες μέλανα
            βροτον ἐξ ὠτειλέων,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 24.189</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            ἀλλά μιν, ἀμφίπολοι, ἀπονίψατε,</span>
