            χρῶτ᾽ ἀπονιψαμένη,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 18.172</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            ἱ̄δρῶ πολλὸν ἀπε̄νίζοντο θαλάσσῃ</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 10.572</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
